   Giving a Hand:
   Ernst &amp; Young Gives Olympic Effort
   To Put U.S. Athletes on Right Track
   ----
   By John A. Conway
</HL>
<DATE>
09/20/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B2
</SO>
<LP>
   {From time to time in this column, The Wall Street Journal
